    public abstract class BoxResource.Info<T extends BoxResource>
extends BoxJSONObject
    Contains additional information about a BoxResource.

    Subclasses should track any changes to a resource's information by calling the BoxJSONObject.addPendingChange(java.lang.String, boolean) method. The pending changes will then be serialized to JSON when BoxJSONObject.getPendingChanges() is called.
